purpose_s: IF asset has any of the terms "competitive", "competitor", "competition" AND user has not role "management", "risk", "product" THEN restrict access

name_s: Restrict access to data for external users
purpose_s: IF asset has term "C2", "C3", "C4", "C5", or doesn't have any classification term assigned AND user domain is not @ataccama.com THEN restrict access
IF asset has term "PII" or term "related to PII" AND user has not role "security" THEN restrict access
IF asset has term "finance" AND user has not role "management", "finance" THEN restrict access
IF asset has term "finance" AND user has not role "management", "finance" THEN restrict access
